The paper presents a method for visualizing the response of a deep neural network to a specific input, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the decision-making process of convolutional networks, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper mentions the potential application of the method in medicine, which could fall under the category of computational biology (cs.CL).
